data.title: Contact Us
data.text:
Main Office

William R. Snodgrass Tennessee Tower

312 Rosa L. Parks Avenue | 23rd Floor

Nashville, Tennessee 37243

Phone: (800) 251-3589

Email: ASK.THRC@tn.gov

Office Hours: Monday - Friday. 8:00am - 4:30pm Central Time.

There are two, 2-hour visitor parking spaces available, parking space numbers 26R and 44R, in state lot 19, behind the Tennessee Supreme Court Building.

Knoxville

7175 Strawberry Plains Pike | Suite 100

Knoxville, Tennessee. 37914

Phone: (800) 251-3589

Email: ASK.THRC@tn.gov

Office Hours: Monday - Friday. 8:00am - 4:30pm Eastern Time.

The Knoxville office is located at the Pellissippi State Community College Strawberry Plains campus.
